dialogues: You need to speak up about how you're feeling, for your own sake.
Gojo-kun, are they taking advantage of you?
Could you look the other way?
She means so much to me, so I want to become her, no matter what!
Cosplaying allows you express just how much you love your faves!
Definitely broke some bones on that landing.
ou just don't go making fun of things people clearly like.
You know how to use a sewing machine, Gojo-kun?
I don't have a sewing machine at home, so I was working on this here after school.
and I don't know anyone who's good at sewing.
Oh! But I'll do everything I can!
The only thing that's lame here is you.
The Young Ladies of the Humiliation Club: Debauched Miracle Life 2!
I mean, he clearly knew it was something I liked before he opened his mouth.
I'm late 'cause I had to go to the bathroom, but I'm on cleaning duty this week.
How do you know how to use one? We don't have home EC as an elective!
It's totally not done yet, but, um...
Not that I can do much!
Yup! I mean, she's just too precious for words!
Like I care about how hot he was.
I just can't deal with guys like him.
Also... how dare he call Shion-tan 'that thing'?!
You shouldn't agree to things you don't wanna do.
No, really. You need to think about yourself more.
Hey, is that a hina doll?
I am not here for question-answering!
I'm still not done with it.
I'm, uh, trying to make that outfit... so, yeah.
I worked really hard on this.
What are you even doing?! Quit it!
But seriously, could you look up?
I made this because I wanted to cosplay!
I want to wear the same things as manga, anime, and game characters!
As you can see, it's not in the best shape,
Will you make me a cosplay outfit?
You can just tell me you can't.
It's not like a cut... right?
I can't do much more on my own.
Shizuku-tan means so much to me...
Ugh. Are you really going to bring that up?
